KitKat2::

She looked at FZ and shook her head. She hadn't heard of Squizzy 
either.  "OK, I'll go and get checked out. I'll be OK."  She headed 
down the hallway but didn't stop at the lab.  She followed her nose 
to the private quarters floor.  She looked around, "Hmmm, I can smell 
my scent here, but how is it that I can't recall being here?"  She 
kept going, gathering the details of the inside of the place as she 
went. Never know when info will come in handy, she thought.
